'''加沙船队冲突'''發生在2010年5月31日的[[地中海|地中海]]上，[[以色列海軍|以色列海軍]]部隊在[[公海|公海]]襲擊了6艘載有國際活動者的船隻，此船隊名為“自由[[加沙|加沙]]船隊”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/may/31/q-a-gaza-freedom-flotilla |title=Q&A: The Gaza Freedom flotilla |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGzNbAy?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/may/31/q-a-gaza-freedom-flotilla |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這些國際活動者計畫突破[[以色列|以色列]]的[[加沙封鎖|加沙封鎖]]以運送人道救援物資到當地。據以色列消息來源，加沙艦隊拒絕改變航向至[[阿什杜德|阿什杜德]]港後，以色列的海軍部隊開始登船，之後以色列強迫船隊航向阿什杜德港並扣留了船上所有的乘員與援助物資，以色列承諾會將檢查過的非違禁援助物資送往加沙<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/israel-gaza-aid-convoy-can-unload-cargo-in-ashdod-for-inspection-1.292560 |title=Israel: Gaza aid convoy can unload cargo in Ashdod for inspection |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2014-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230235746/http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/israel-gaza-aid-convoy-can-unload-cargo-in-ashdod-for-inspection-1.292560 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在懸掛[[葛摩|葛摩]]旗幟的[[藍色馬爾馬拉號|藍色馬爾馬拉號]]船上，有9名乘客遭登船以軍殺害，另1名重傷乘客昏迷4年後不治死亡。<ref name="tenth_in_2014"/>在衝突中有60名船隊乘員和10名[[以色列國防軍|以色列國防軍]]軍人受傷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703703704575277632709673018.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_LEADNewsCollection |title=Flotilla Assault Spurs Crisis |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603122225/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703703704575277632709673018.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_LEADNewsCollection |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/israel-navy-commandos-gaza-flotilla-activists-tried-to-lynch-us-1.293089 |title=Flotilla Assault Spurs Crisis |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2015-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607140739/http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/israel-navy-commandos-gaza-flotilla-activists-tried-to-lynch-us-1.293089 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

以色列聲稱，其士兵遭小刀和金屬條伏擊，還被奪走手槍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/meast/05/31/gaza.protest/index.html?hpt=T1 |title=Israeli assault on Gaza-bound flotilla leaves at least 9 dead |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603211209/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/meast/05/31/gaza.protest/index.html?hpt=T1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>國際之間強烈批評以色列的行動，並為死傷者深感遺憾，要求調查衝突經過。[[聯合國安理會|聯合國安理會]]也譴責此次事件至少造成10名平民死亡並有多人受傷，並呼籲要迅速公正的調查衝突<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2010/sc9940.doc.htm |title=UN News |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2010-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100604052317/http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2010/sc9940.doc.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

以色列總理[[本雅明·內塔尼亞胡|本雅明·內塔尼亞胡]]稱這次事件為[[正當防衛|正當防衛]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pmo.gov.il/PMOEng/Communication/Spokesman/2010/06/spokehatshara010610.htm |title=Statement by PM Netanyahu Regarding Flotilla to Gaza |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2010-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605042336/http://www.pmo.gov.il/PMOEng/Communication/Spokesman/2010/06/spokehatshara010610.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。以色列表示將釋放50名乘客和船員，其餘629名拒絕透露身份者則被監禁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/06/01/palestine-militants-fight_n_595666.html |title=Palestine Militants Fight Israel, Two Reported Dead |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2010-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602043043/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/06/01/palestine-militants-fight_n_595666.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
{{main|自由加薩運動}}
